315
00:15:18,070 --> 00:15:19,030
I never would have thought

316
00:15:20,250 --> 00:15:23,650
Mi Lan was a Japanese spy.

317
00:15:24,870 --> 00:15:25,620
Uncle Yang,

318
00:15:28,540 --> 00:15:29,340
you don't know

319
00:15:32,090 --> 00:15:34,040
how much I doubted myself

320
00:15:35,230 --> 00:15:36,350
when I came home

321
00:15:38,470 --> 00:15:40,690
and saw Grandma.

322
00:15:42,270 --> 00:15:43,120
I felt deeply unsure—

323
00:15:44,470 --> 00:15:45,270
unsure whether I had

324
00:15:46,440 --> 00:15:47,800
what it takes to stand

325
00:15:47,830 --> 00:15:48,950
against Kunwu,

326
00:15:51,350 --> 00:15:52,390
unsure whether

327
00:15:54,510 --> 00:15:55,900
I could fulfill my father's

328
