332
00:16:09,510 --> 00:16:10,110
Hongshen.

333
00:16:11,620 --> 00:16:12,730
Don't doubt yourself.

334
00:16:14,030 --> 00:16:15,390
You've already become

335
00:16:15,400 --> 00:16:17,620
an exceptionally outstanding fighter.

336
00:16:27,070 --> 00:16:29,830
The calmness and patience you used to lack—

337
00:16:30,070 --> 00:16:31,380
