343
00:16:42,230 --> 00:16:44,430
you will successfully complete the mission

344
00:16:44,450 --> 00:16:45,900
Muzhi left behind.

345
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:49,650
If Muzhi were still here

346
00:16:51,670 --> 00:16:53,260
and saw the progress you've made,

347
00:16:56,040 --> 00:16:57,200
he'd be incredibly proud.

348
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:04,119
If I'd discovered Mi Lan's issue earlier,

349
00:17:08,380 --> 00:17:09,990
Grandma wouldn't have been harmed.

350
00:17:12,300 --> 00:17:13,300
This is all my fault.

351
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:23,680
Hongshen,

352
00:17:24,089 --> 00:17:26,359
I understand the pain

353
