360
00:17:56,830 --> 00:17:59,270
warmth and support as I grew up.

361
00:17:59,840 --> 00:18:01,400
When Muzhi was dying,

362
00:18:01,430 --> 00:18:02,810
he entrusted her care to me,

363
00:18:03,460 --> 00:18:04,700
but I failed.

364
00:18:06,230 --> 00:18:07,390
I let both Muzhi

365
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:09,850
and Aunt Yun down.

366
00:18:19,480 --> 00:18:20,200
