375
00:18:49,870 --> 00:18:52,520
So, your decision not to act against her for now was right.

376
00:18:52,930 --> 00:18:54,440
She might be our

377
00:18:54,470 --> 00:18:56,470
best chance to find Kunwu.

378
00:18:56,620 --> 00:18:57,590
However, one thing

379
00:18:57,840 --> 00:18:58,880
deeply unsettles me—

380
00:18:59,670 --> 00:19:01,380
Myna stole intelligence from the Japanese,

381
00:19:01,380 --> 00:19:04,270
yet his daughter turned out to be a Japanese spy.

382
00:19:04,960 --> 00:19:06,030
This is too strange.

383
00:19:08,170 --> 00:19:08,860
Uncle Yang,

384
00:19:11,100 --> 00:19:12,870
