385
00:19:13,580 --> 00:19:15,470
Why would my father risk his life

386
00:19:16,930 --> 00:19:18,440
to get that message out?

387
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:21,230
What exactly was the message?

388
00:19:21,960 --> 00:19:23,360
What was he suspicious of?

389
00:19:23,780 --> 00:19:24,500
Hongshen,

390
00:19:26,460 --> 00:19:27,590
you truly are smart.

391
00:19:28,430 --> 00:19:29,870
Muzhi would be proud of you.

392
00:19:31,790 --> 00:19:32,470
But we've

393
00:19:33,440 --> 00:19:35,840
