396
00:19:44,320 --> 00:19:44,960
Understood.

397
00:19:46,630 --> 00:19:47,430
Uncle Yang,

398
00:19:48,580 --> 00:19:49,420
I'd like to

399
00:19:50,500 --> 00:19:51,880
