409
00:20:19,270 --> 00:20:19,910
Of course.

410
00:20:20,550 --> 00:20:21,870
As I said earlier,

411
00:20:22,750 --> 00:20:23,770
you've already become

412
00:20:23,790 --> 00:20:25,860
an exceptionally outstanding fighter.

413
00:20:26,750 --> 00:20:27,470
Let me

414
00:20:28,620 --> 00:20:30,570
be your introducer to the Party.

415
00:20:31,190 --> 00:20:32,390
We'll formally submit

416
00:20:32,410 --> 00:20:33,620
our application to the Party.

417
00:20:34,050 --> 00:20:35,370
But, Hongshen, you must understand

418
00:20:35,580 --> 00:20:38,140
that the Party has very strict discipline.

419
00:20:38,590 --> 00:20:39,670
From now on,

420
00:20:39,990 --> 00:20:41,350
you need to hold yourself

421
00:20:41,390 --> 00:20:42,790
to an even higher standard.

422
00:20:43,090 --> 00:20:44,810
You must follow the Party's commands in everything

423
00:20:45,350 --> 00:20:47,510
and never act without organization or discipline.

424
00:20:47,570 --> 00:20:48,240
Do you understand?

425
00:20:49,430 --> 00:20:50,190
I understand.

426
00:20:53,130 --> 00:20:54,720
But there's still a problem.

427
00:20:55,270 --> 00:20:56,110
What problem?

428
00:20:56,390 --> 00:20:57,340
