456
00:23:03,910 --> 00:23:05,110
Mi Lan is so simple and pure.

457
00:23:05,240 --> 00:23:06,330
There's no way it's her.

458
00:23:07,030 --> 00:23:07,990
She's timid.

459
00:23:08,020 --> 00:23:09,450
She wouldn't dare do something like this.

460
00:23:09,750 --> 00:23:10,700
It's the Bai family.

461
00:23:10,990 --> 00:23:12,150
Jingyu already told me.

462
00:23:12,310 --> 00:23:13,750
Gui wanted to pull me into their business,

463
00:23:13,830 --> 00:23:14,910
but Grandma refused.

464
00:23:15,100 --> 00:23:16,310
She held a grudge because of it.

465
00:23:16,350 --> 00:23:18,600
She's also bitter about the closure of Happy House.

466
00:23:18,790 --> 00:23:20,230
That's why she resorted to desperate measures.

467
00:23:20,330 --> 00:23:20,870
That's why she...

468
00:23:20,870 --> 00:23:22,310
Unless Mrs. Jin wants to risk everything,

469
00:23:22,590 --> 00:23:24,140
there's no way she'd harm Grandma.

470
00:23:28,270 --> 00:23:28,990
Shen,

471
00:23:29,960 --> 00:23:30,840
Gui...

472
00:23:31,510 --> 00:23:32,040
She...

473
00:23:32,960 --> 00:23:34,170
She panicked.

474
00:23:34,370 --> 00:23:36,110
She took a reckless gamble.

475
00:23:36,190 --> 00:23:37,780
It's entirely possible she did this.

476
00:23:38,130 --> 00:23:39,290
Mrs. Jin's bodyguard

477
00:23:40,690 --> 00:23:41,890
has already been silenced.

478
00:23:47,630 --> 00:23:48,340
Impossible.

479
00:23:49,520 --> 00:23:50,330
-It's impossible.
-Hongqi.

480
00:23:51,200 --> 00:23:52,480
I know it's hard to accept,

481
00:23:53,290 --> 00:23:54,960
but why would Uncle Yang and I lie to you?

482
00:24:00,590 --> 00:24:01,310
You're mistaken.

483
00:24:04,260 --> 00:24:05,230
You've got it wrong.

484
00:24:05,740 --> 00:24:07,220
It must be a mistake.

485
00:24:08,340 --> 00:24:09,260
You're mistaken.

