488
00:24:14,320 --> 00:24:16,170
You're the last person I'd want to see hurt.

489
00:24:16,780 --> 00:24:18,410
I would never lie to you.

490
00:24:20,470 --> 00:24:22,240
I wish none of this were true as well.

491
00:24:24,830 --> 00:24:25,700
