493
00:24:42,900 --> 00:24:44,900
The focus should be on Mi Lan's past social connections,

494
00:24:45,700 --> 00:24:47,710
the suspicious individuals she interacted with,

495
00:24:48,030 --> 00:24:49,590
and when she was turned.

496
00:24:49,790 --> 00:24:51,390
The details you provide must be as thorough as possible.

497
00:24:52,090 --> 00:24:52,500
And remember,

498
00:24:52,520 --> 00:24:53,950
if you can include specific evidence

499
00:24:53,970 --> 00:24:55,010
to back it up,

500
00:24:55,230 --> 00:24:56,270
that would be ideal.

501
00:24:56,480 --> 00:24:57,630
Understood.

502
00:25:21,750 --> 00:25:23,150
I brought this on Grandma.

503
00:25:31,070 --> 00:25:34,320
I let the wolf into the house.

504
00:25:41,790 --> 00:25:42,310
Hongqi!

505
00:26:41,280 --> 00:26:43,350
[Yun Residence]

506
00:26:58,980 --> 00:26:59,860
Get me Director Dai.

507
00:27:02,940 --> 00:27:03,470
Director,

508
00:27:03,780 --> 00:27:04,580
