00:27:39,230 --> 00:27:40,080
Keep a close watch.

519
00:27:40,470 --> 00:27:41,270
Monitor it closely.

520
00:27:42,600 --> 00:27:43,840
The emergence of

521
00:27:44,410 --> 00:27:45,680
a new radio station at a time like this

522
00:27:47,100 --> 00:27:48,530
is no small matter.

523
00:27:48,750 --> 00:27:49,350
Yes, sir.

524
00:28:36,570 --> 00:28:37,170
Mengying,

525
00:28:37,470 --> 00:28:38,470
how many clothes did you wash?

526
00:28:38,490 --> 00:28:39,450
