527
00:28:40,360 --> 00:28:41,670
Better to wash early than late.

528
00:28:42,260 --> 00:28:43,500
The work has to be done anyway.

529
00:28:43,840 --> 00:28:44,570
Mengying,

530
00:28:45,110 --> 00:28:46,180
you're unusually diligent today.

531
00:28:46,490 --> 00:28:47,730
