559
00:29:42,340 --> 00:29:42,910
Go to sleep soon.

560
00:29:48,320 --> 00:29:48,940
Oh, by the way,

561
00:29:50,150 --> 00:29:51,910
Gui came to the bureau today to see me.

562
00:29:52,350 --> 00:29:53,780
She said something strange.

563
00:29:53,980 --> 00:29:57,420
